msgstr "Inne ustawienia kursu"

#: xmodule/course_block.py:1058
msgid ""
"Any additional information about the course that the platform needs or that "
"allows integration with external systems such as CRM software. Enter a "
"dictionary of values in JSON format, such as { \"my_custom_setting\": "
"\"value\", \"other_setting\": \"value\" }"
msgstr ""
"Wszelkie dodatkowe informacje o kursie, które są potrzebne platformie lub "
"umożliwiają integrację z systemami zewnętrznymi, takimi jak CRM. Wprowadź "
"słownik wartości w formacie JSON, np. { \"my_custom_setting\": \"value\", "
"\"other_setting\": \"value\" }"

#: xmodule/course_block.py:1110
msgid "General"
msgstr "Ogólne"

